# Vercel deployment

This Next.js app is intended to deploy on **Vercel**. Connect the GitHub repo in the Vercel dashboard, import the project, and use the default settings (framework: Next.js, `npm run build`, output handled by Vercel).

Pushes to the connected branch (e.g. `main`) trigger production deploys when Git integration is enabled.

If `render.yaml` is still in the repo, it is legacy from Render; **Vercel does not use it** for builds.
